                     <interp inst="t17490906-57-person341" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was drinking in the house; while I was lighting my pipe by the candle, the prisoner run away with the tankard .</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17490906-57-person342">
                  Samuel 
                  Gear 
               <interp inst="t17490906-57-person342" type="surname" value="Gear"></interp>
