            , where the prisoner confessed the taking of it.</p>
               <p>The prosecutor, and the prosecutor's father in law a dyer, with whom the prisoner worked as a <rs id="t17490906-57-deflabel229" type="occupation">servant</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17490906-57-defend337 t17490906-57-deflabel229"></join> , and others spoke well of him as to his former character .</p>
